title: The Dark at the Top of the Stairs.mp4
description:
Video quality is flaky; it's from a DVD of a broadcast or some such thing. I was amazed to find it available ANYWHERE. 

I've been looking for it for years.

So now that I've got this one (a lot better than nothing), I wanted to share it.

Probably anyone searching for this title already knows how excellent it is. Why it's not available (anywhere ELSE) is a mystery to me
